"><div class="media-object-rich-text"><h4> MORE IN OFF DUTY TRAVEL</h4><ul class="articleList"><li> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/a-nevada-town-where-the-west-is-still-wild-49ec4045?mod=article_relatedinline" target="_blank" class="icon none">A Nevada Town Where the West Is Still Wild</a></li><li> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/a-locals-guide-to-san-diego-the-insider-spots-most-visitors-miss-cb5cd050?mod=article_relatedinline&amp;mod=article_relatedinline" target="_blank" class="icon none">A Locals&#39; Guide to San Diego: The Insider Spots Most Visitors Miss</a></li><li> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/a-spiritual-journey-exploring-portugals-hidden-jewish-history-670e2771?mod=article_relatedinline&amp;mod=article_relatedinline" target="_blank" class="icon none">A Spiritual Journey: Exploring Portugal&#39;s Hidden Jewish History</a></li><li> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/last-minute-summer-vacation-ideas-c480f358?mod=article_relatedinline&amp;mod=article_relatedinline" target="_blank" class="icon none">The Procrastinator&#39;s Guide to a (Truly Great) Last-Minute Summer Vacation</a></li><li> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/carmel-by-the-sea-california-storybook-charm-architecture-dbe5c880?mod=article_relatedinline&amp;mod=article_relatedinline" target="_blank" class="icon none">For 1920s Storybook Charm, Escape to California&#39;s Carmel-by-the-Sea</a></li></ul></div></div></section></div></main></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Tue, 08 Aug 2023 20:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.wsj.com/articles/around-the-world-in-24-days-is-a-luxury-jet-cruise-for-you-ea66dd1f</guid><link/> https://www.wsj.com/articles/around-the-world-in-24-days-is-a-luxury-jet-cruise-for-you-ea66dd1f<category> off duty</category><category>政治/一般新闻</category><category>Cruises</category><category> Living/Lifestyle</category><category> Travel</category><category> SYND</category><category>华尔街日报-PRO-WSJ.com</category><category>政治的</categor